<color=yellow>DEBUG CONTROLS</color>

B+D+Enter = Debug mode (Toggleable)
B+D+P = Toggle Output Log (Toggleable)
B+D+G = 100x Speed (Toggleable)
B+D+H = 0.1x Speed (Toggleable)
F8 = Save previous error to TXT file
ALT+F4 = Unlock all secrets and logs
Key_Up = Refresh Current Chatbox
Key_Left = Advance Backwards in Chatbox
